## Troubleshooting

### Widgets never appear

- Confirm **`inlineMedia_core.js`** finished loading (network tab, no blocked third-party scripts).
- Confirm **`initializeInline`** runs **after** all `myFinance-widget` nodes exist in the document. If your framework mounts placeholders asynchronously, call **`initializeInline` again** after they render (if supported) or move initialization to a lifecycle hook that runs after placeholders exist.

### Wrong or empty widget

- Verify **`data-ad-id`**, **`data-campaign`**, and **`data-s1`** match what Bankrate issued for your integration. Replace **`PLACESUBIDHERE`** with your real sub-ID.

### Styling / layout

- **`overwriteContainer: true`** lets the embed manage its container. If layout conflicts with your CSS, work with your Bankrate contact before changing integration flags.

